# Vercel Ignore File
# Prevent unnecessary build triggers by ignoring files that don't affect the build

# Documentation
/DOCUMENTACIÓN/
/docs/

*.md
!README.md

# Scripts & Data
/scripts/

cache/
# Configuration
!**/*.json


# Local / Temp
.temp/
tmp/
.DS_Store
*.log

# Git
.git/
.github/
.gitignore
.gitmodules
